{
  "stem": "23090.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They wanted to extract all the, the values-- the valuables from the people, I mean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I lived this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came next door, they came down the street, they came to my cousins, they came to my friends' parents.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I lived that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It isn't something I read about.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That isn't something that someone told me, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know it, and I've lived it, OK?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- And that was the conversation in the house always.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], they beat him, and they took him, and they did this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took him down to Gestapo headquarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the next time you saw [INAUDIBLE], he was like a vegetable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it isn't something that, that, that you have-- that, you know, see on television, which of course, was nonexistent at the time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it's something that you lived on a daily basis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Since you-- we all lived as a very close community, you had the opportunity to see it and observe it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You saw [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] specific people who were taken by the Germans?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw them being taken, uncles of mine, and, and friends' parents, and they would come back a few days later with, with, with just-- or some never came back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but those that came back were beaten to a-- to a-- to a pulp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a method to-- it was a method to the madness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the thing is give it up, you shouldn't have it, and you're better off giving it now without being-- without this happening to you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was always a lesson.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The great lesson in the Lodz ghetto was that each time someone committed something like that or against something that was the rule, it was to bring everybody out on a marktplatz.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
